Add a .rowId column to a data frame

Source: R/helpers.R
dot-create_rowid.Rd

Add a .rowId column to a data frame

Usage

.create_rowid(data, rowId = NULL)

Arguments

data

A data frame

rowId

The name of the primary key column

Value

data with a new column named .rowId at column position one that has an MD5 hash uniquely identifying that row

Examples

faketables:::.create_rowid(mtcars)
